<div data-collapse="medium" data-animation="default" data-duration="400" data-easing="ease" data-easing2="ease" data-doc-height="1" role="banner" class="header-navigation w-nav"><div class="header-navigation-container-2"><div class="w-layout-grid navigation-bar-grid"><div id="w-node-_7bd6a3b1-d92a-adc1-0d76-21df00078a8a-de0ea221" class="nav-left-grid-block"><div data-w-id="7bd6a3b1-d92a-adc1-0d76-21df00078a8b" class="menu-button-3"><div class="menu-lines"><div class="navbar-menu-line-2 move"></div><div class="toggle-spacer"></div><div class="navbar-menu-line-2"></div></div></div></div><div id="w-node-_7bd6a3b1-d92a-adc1-0d76-21df00078a90-de0ea221" class="nav-middle-grid-block"><a href="#" id="w-node-_7bd6a3b1-d92a-adc1-0d76-21df00078a91-de0ea221" class="logo-image-wrapper w-inline-block"><img src="/img/horizontal-long-white.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" height="50" class="image"/></a></div><div id="w-node-_7bd6a3b1-d92a-adc1-0d76-21df00078a93-de0ea221" class="nav-right-grid-block mobile-hide"></div></div><div data-scroll="stop" class="side-menu-container-2"><div class="side-menu-links-wrapper-2"><div class="side-menu-links-container"><div data-w-id="7bd6a3b1-d92a-adc1-0d76-21df00078a9f" class="image-wrapper nav-x-icon"><img loading="lazy" src="/img/x.svg" alt="X icon." class="inner-nav-logo"/></div><div class="side-menu"><div class="footer-links-wrapper header"><a href="https://docs.filbeam.com" class="footer-link-2 header">Docs</a><a href="https://dashboard.filbeam.com" class="footer-link-2 header-copy">Dashboard</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="page-wrapper"><div class="inner-page-wrapper home"><section class="section overflow-hidden"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container white-text purple-brain top-header w-container"><div class="w-layout-grid content-grid purple-brain display-none-tablet"><div class="grid-block"><div class="content-wrapper purple-brain-left home"><h1 class="h1-heading about-hero mobile">Filecoin Beam</h1><p class="paragraph gray">The incentivized data delivery layer for Filecoin</p><div class="text-box"><div class="text-box _19rem gray home"><div class="w-layout-hflex flex-block-2"><img src="/img/fil-pl-logo.svg" loading="lazy" alt="filecoin and protocol labs logo"/><div class="heading-7 mobile">A Filecoin project, supported by Protocol Labs</div></div></div></div><div class="button-container header"><a href="https://docs.filbeam.com" class="button-link-block-3 black hero-section w-inline-block"><div class="button-block _01 header"><div class="text-block-3">Get Started</div></div></a></div></div></div><div class="grid-block"><div class="content-wrapper purple-brain-right header"><img src="/img/header-illustration.avif" loading="lazy" alt="" class="image-2"/></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section overflow-hidden"><div class="hero-lines-container home"><div class="vertical-line hero"></div><div class="vertical-line hero"></div><div class="vertical-line hero"></div><div class="vertical-line hero no-right-border-mobile"></div><div class="vertical-line hero no-right-border-mobile"></div><div class="vertical-line hero no-right-border-mobile"></div></div><div class="image-wrapper hero-main"></div></section><section class="section station-checker home callout"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-two w-container"><h2 class="h2-heading two-column-size callout mobile small">Filecoin Beam is the incentivized data delivery layer for Filecoin. Storage Providers for the first time can be paid in the protocol for serving data to clients. </h2></div></section><section class="section scroll"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container sticky-cards home w-container"><div class="services-content-wrapper"><div id="w-node-_70124cf0-d9a4-4f61-2c64-5bf2c501a080-181e7cb0" class="sticky-services-left-block"><div class="text-box sticky-cards-left"><h2 class="h2-heading two-column-size home-section-5"><span class="gradient-text"><em>Filecoin Beam</em> </span>makes data delivery seamless and advantageous for both the clients and the providers.</h2></div></div><div id="w-node-_70124cf0-d9a4-4f61-2c64-5bf2c501a089-181e7cb0" class="services-right-block"><div class="grid-block"><div class="services-content-block home"><div id="w-node-_70124cf0-d9a4-4f61-2c64-5bf2c501a08c-181e7cb0" class="image-wrapper services-right-block home"><img loading="lazy" src="/img/frame-17.svg" alt="" class="content-image team-member-full absolute home"/></div><div id="w-node-_70124cf0-d9a4-4f61-2c64-5bf2c501a08e-181e7cb0" class="grid-block"><div class="text-box z-index-2"><h3 class="h3-heading medium"><span class="top-box">For Clients</span></h3><div class="text-box _19rem darker-gray wide"><p class="paragraph gray no-margin"><strong>One URL, Zero Hassle:</strong> Access all PDP content via <code>filbeam.io</code>.<br/><br/>‍<strong>Instant Global Speed:</strong> Consumer-grade performance, anywhere.<br/><br/>‍<strong>Always-On Reliability:</strong> Your cached data stays online, even if Service Providers are temporarily down.</p></div></div></div><div class="card-number-circle sticky-cards home"><div>01</div></div></div></div><div class="services-content-block home"><div id="w-node-_70124cf0-d9a4-4f61-2c64-5bf2c501a09d-181e7cb0" class="image-wrapper services-right-block home"><img id="w-node-_70124cf0-d9a4-4f61-2c64-5bf2c501a09e-181e7cb0" loading="lazy" alt="" src="/img/frame-18.svg" class="content-image team-member-full absolute home"/></div><div id="w-node-_70124cf0-d9a4-4f61-2c64-5bf2c501a09f-181e7cb0" class="grid-block"><div class="text-box z-index-2"><h3 class="h3-heading medium">For Providers</h3><div class="text-box _19rem darker-gray wide"><p class="paragraph gray no-margin"><strong>Security First: </strong>Shields you from DDoS, scraping, and bad traffic.<br/><br/>‍<strong>Get Paid to Serve:</strong> Earn rewards for serving data.<br/><br/>‍<strong>Trustless by Design:</strong> Paid-per-byte for storage <em>and</em> retrieval.</p></div></div></div><div class="card-number-circle sticky-cards home"><div>02</div></div></div><div class="grid-block"><div class="services-content-block home"><div id="w-node-_70124cf0-d9a4-4f61-2c64-5bf2c501a0ab-181e7cb0" class="image-wrapper services-right-block home"><img loading="lazy" src="/img/frame-19.svg" alt="" class="content-image team-member-full absolute home"/></div><div id="w-node-_70124cf0-d9a4-4f61-2c64-5bf2c501a0ad-181e7cb0" class="grid-block"><div class="text-box z-index-2"><h3 class="h3-heading medium _03">For Network Health</h3><div class="text-box _19rem darker-gray wide"><p class="paragraph gray no-margin">All Filecoin Beam retrieval data is submitted on chain so that clients can make informed decisions about which providers to do business with </p></div></div></div><div class="card-number-circle sticky-cards home"><div>03</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section"></section><section class="section small-top-margin"><div class="top-of-section-container general white"><div class="top-content-block-container"><div class="content-wrapper top-block"><div class="content-block home-boxes"><div class="top-block-eyebrow home">Roadmap</div></div><div class="content-block right-aligned"></div></div></div></div><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer text-boxes w-container"><div class="number-stat-cards-container"><div class="numbered-stat-card-wrapper right-border left-side"><div class="text-box sticky-product-02-intro"><h3 class="h3-heading intro-cards about-03-stat-card home-boxes">Q3 2025</h3><p class="paragraph _4rem-bottom-margin home-boxes mobile">✅ Launch: Filecoin Beam on Filecoin CalibrationNet<br/>✅ Payments: payment channels on Filecoin for egress<br/>📆 Launch: Filecoin Beam on Filecoin Mainnet<br/><br/></p></div><div class="stat-number-wrapper"></div></div><div class="numbered-stat-card-wrapper right-border"><div class="text-box sticky-product-02-intro"><h3 class="h3-heading intro-cards about-03-stat-card home-boxes">Q4 2025</h3><div class="text-box _19rem gray"><p class="paragraph _4rem-bottom-margin home-boxes">🚧 Payments: Metered egress pricing plan<br/>🚧 Payments: Requester pays to retrieve model<br/>📆 Launch: Filecoin Beam General Access as part of Filecoin Onchain Cloud</p></div></div><div class="stat-number-wrapper"></div></div><div class="numbered-stat-card-wrapper right-border"><div class="text-box sticky-product-02-intro"><h3 class="h3-heading intro-cards about-03-stat-card home-boxes">Q1 2026</h3><div class="text-box _19rem gray"><p class="paragraph _4rem-bottom-margin home-boxes">🚧 Feature: IPFS Interoperability<br/>🚧 Feature: x402 implementation<br/>🚧 Feature: Access Control<br/></p></div></div></div><div class="numbered-stat-card-wrapper right-border right-end"><div class="text-box sticky-product-02-intro"><h3 class="h3-heading intro-cards about-03-stat-card home-boxes">Q2 2026</h3><div class="text-box _19rem gray"><p class="paragraph _4rem-bottom-margin home-boxes">🚧 Feature: Erasure coding reconstruction<br/>🚧 Payments: Pay per byte protocol integrated<br/>🚧 Node: v1 Filecoin Beam node offering</p></div></div><div class="stat-number-wrapper"></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section funding"><div id="w-node-_7fa8455d-f1b8-4bbe-68bc-0cca21113063-181e7cb0" class="w-layout-layout quick-stack mobile wf-layout-layout"><div class="w-layout-cell cell funding mobile"><div class="logo-column-title services-eyebrow _02 gradient-text logo-strip">Funding Partners</div></div><div class="w-layout-cell cell logo mobile"><img decoding="async" height="45" alt="" src="/img/filecoin-foundation-logo.svg" loading="eager" class="marquee-horizontal-logo-image"/></div><div class="w-layout-cell cell logo mobile"><img width="68" height="45" alt="" src="/img/pl-vs-logo.svg" loading="eager" decoding="async" class="marquee-horizontal-logo-image"/></div><div class="w-layout-cell cell logo mobile"><img width="68" height="45" alt="" src="/img/image-27.svg" loading="eager" decoding="async" class="ma